Episodes.
Season 3 (2012-2013).
With 20 episodes having been produced for Season 3, the second part of the season is being referred to as Season 3B. It premiered on January 16, 2013. 
Future Seasons.
On January 6, 2013, Comedy Central renewed "Workaholics" for a 4th and 5th season, consisting of 13 episodes each.
